# 🌐 1️⃣ What Does "Deploying an Application" Mean?

### Simple Definition

Deployment means:

> Making your application available to real users on the internet.

---

### Before Deployment

```text
Your Laptop
    ↓
Only you can use it
```

---

### After Deployment

```text
Internet
    ↓
Anyone can access it
```

---

### Mental Model 🧠

Building a restaurant is development.

Opening it to customers is deployment.

---

# 🌐 2️⃣ Domain vs Hosting

This is one of the most commonly misunderstood concepts.

---

## What is a Domain?

A domain is the human-friendly name.

Examples:

* [google.com](https://google.com?utm_source=chatgpt.com)
* [github.com](https://github.com?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

---

### Mental Model

Domain = House Address 🏠

Example:

```text
123 Main Street
```

---

## What is Hosting?

Hosting is the computer/server where your application lives.

---

### Mental Model

Hosting = Actual House

Domain = Address of the house

---

### Memory Trick

**Domain tells WHERE**

**Hosting stores WHAT**

---

# 🌐 3️⃣ How DNS Fits In

Let's connect this with what you've already learned.

---

When a user enters:

```text
mywebsite.com
```

DNS converts:

```text
mywebsite.com
        ↓
  IP Address
```

Browser then connects to the server.

---

### Complete Flow

```text
User
 ↓
Domain Name
 ↓
DNS
 ↓
IP Address
 ↓
Hosting Server
 ↓
Website Loads
```

---

### Why This Is Important

This connects:

✅ DNS
✅ HTTP
✅ Hosting
✅ Deployment

into one complete picture.

